    "title": "H&M India is Hiring: Floor Manager (Principal)",
    "description": "Grow your career with H&M India! We are hiring a Floor Manager for our Srinagar team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout H&M India:\nH&M India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Loss Prevention\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with H&M India!",
